'''Jean-Pierre Poly''' (b. 1941) is a French historian. He was the student of [[Georges Duby]], and he was graduated on History in 1972.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.univ-nancy2.fr/clhd/informations/agregation.html |title=Concours d'agrégation d'histoire du droit |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110220183508/http://www.univ-nancy2.fr/clhd/informations/agregation.html |archive-date=20 February 2011 |work=[[Université de Lorraine]] |date=14 February 2007 |publisher=[[Université Nancy 2]]}}</ref> He is specialized in [[feudalism]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sudoc.fr/084415592 |title=La Société féodale en Provence du Xe au XIIe siècle. Contribution à l'étude des structures féodales dans le midi de la Gaule |first=Jean-Pierre |last=Poly |year=1972 |oclc=492268525}}</ref>

